::Prowl/Hot Rod/Epyon/Skyburst::

Prowl looks to Skyburst and Prowl.
"Help move Nighstrike to a cell. Also Nightstrike, stick around, I'd
like to talk to you when I get back."
He turns to Hot Rod.
"Let's go meet these new bots, that our asking for help."

"Ok, lets go," said Hot Rod, as he and Prowl made their way out of the
city. 
Hot Rod transformed to car mode, and drove off, in the direction of the
new bots. 
"Prowl, beast mode," said Prowl as he transformed to his owl/raptor
mode, and flew in the same direction. Prowl opened a comm link to the
bots.
"This is Commander Prowl of the Maximals. Myself and one of my troops
are heading your way."

Back at the city, Epyon and Skyburst lifted Nightstrike, and started
moveing towards a cell.

OOC: Airly, I think you wanted Nightstrike to escape right? Now is your
chance.
